1194
00:45:01,719 --> 00:45:03,159
I have animal handling.

1195
00:45:03,159 --> 00:45:05,039
I'm proficient in animal handling.

1196
00:45:05,039 --> 00:45:05,880
Okay.

1197
00:45:05,880 --> 00:45:07,400
I also have animal handling.

1198
00:45:07,400 --> 00:45:08,759
Okay.

1199
00:45:08,759 --> 00:45:09,599
So.

1200
00:45:09,599 --> 00:45:10,639
I also have a minus

1201
00:45:10,639 --> 00:45:12,599
to my animal handling ability.

1202
00:45:12,599 --> 00:45:14,559
You stay back.

1203
00:45:14,559 --> 00:45:15,400
All right.

1204
00:45:15,400 --> 00:45:16,239
You stay back.

1205
00:45:16,239 --> 00:45:18,400
I think maybe we get them to stop barking.

1206
00:45:18,400 --> 00:45:19,800
We befriend them and we're like,

1207
00:45:19,800 --> 00:45:20,800
it's okay, puppy dogs.

1208
00:45:20,800 --> 00:45:22,840
Because we don't want to alert the town

1209
00:45:22,840 --> 00:45:26,440
and barking dogs make people unsteady.

1210
00:45:26,440 --> 00:45:27,280
Makes sense.

1211
00:45:27,280 --> 00:45:28,100
Yeah.

1212
00:45:28,100 --> 00:45:28,940
So.

1213
00:45:28,940 --> 00:45:30,600
Eight plus seven.

1214
00:45:30,600 --> 00:45:31,440
Are you the only one?

1215
00:45:31,440 --> 00:45:33,240
New Laura, are you doing this as well?

1216
00:45:33,240 --> 00:45:34,079
Yeah.

1217
00:45:34,079 --> 00:45:35,280
I also have.

1218
00:45:35,280 --> 00:45:37,680
So if you have, if I have proficiency,

1219
00:45:37,680 --> 00:45:39,440
I just add my proficiency bonus

1220
00:45:39,440 --> 00:45:41,920
or do I also add like my,

1221
00:45:43,240 --> 00:45:45,079
I guess wisdom bonus.

1222
00:45:45,079 --> 00:45:48,600
You would add your wisdom and your proficiency bonus.

1223
00:45:48,600 --> 00:45:49,440
You know what?

1224
00:45:49,440 --> 00:45:50,640
On your character sheet,

1225
00:45:50,640 --> 00:45:52,720
beside where it says animal handling,

1226
00:45:53,600 --> 00:45:56,120
it gives you a number and that's your bonus.

1227
00:45:56,120 --> 00:45:57,120
This is factual.

1228
00:45:57,120 --> 00:45:58,080
Does it.

1229
00:45:58,080 --> 00:45:59,400
Does it now.

1230
00:45:59,400 --> 00:46:02,360
I rolled a 16 plus five.

1231
00:46:02,360 --> 00:46:03,200
So 21.

1232
00:46:03,200 --> 00:46:05,360
You're trying to calm down the dogs

1233
00:46:05,360 --> 00:46:08,480
and you're somewhat successful,

1234
00:46:08,480 --> 00:46:12,000
but you hear almost as soon as you start doing this,

1235
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:13,840
