1237
00:46:15,120 --> 00:46:19,800
And you are greeted by a whole slew of warriors.

1238
00:46:19,800 --> 00:46:21,880
There are 25 warriors,

1239
00:46:21,920 --> 00:46:23,519
30 commoners.

1240
00:46:23,519 --> 00:46:27,960
And there's also three people who are more dressed up

1241
00:46:27,960 --> 00:46:30,320
