1242
00:46:30,320 --> 00:46:33,079
I remain like sitting on the floor,

1243
00:46:33,079 --> 00:46:35,280
on the ground surrounded by the dogs.

1244
00:46:35,280 --> 00:46:36,880
And I've like got one laying down

1245
00:46:36,880 --> 00:46:38,160
and I'm scratching its belly.

1246
00:46:38,160 --> 00:46:39,000
That's how.

1247
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:40,000
You didn't succeed that well.

1248
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:40,840
What?

1249
00:46:40,840 --> 00:46:41,760
Why not?

1250
00:46:41,760 --> 00:46:42,599
Can I pet them?

1251
00:46:42,599 --> 00:46:43,680
Am I petting them?

1252
00:46:43,680 --> 00:46:45,440
I just remain off in the background,

1253
00:46:45,440 --> 00:46:48,640
not talking to the dogs at all.

1254
00:46:48,640 --> 00:46:51,320
So you are greeted by a whole bunch of people.

1255
00:46:51,320 --> 00:46:53,400
The warriors have weapons drawn

1256
00:46:53,400 --> 00:46:56,880
and they begin yelling at you in their language.

1257
00:46:56,880 --> 00:46:58,360
Yulia, what do you do?

1258
00:46:59,360 --> 00:47:00,200
I wave.

1259
00:47:00,200 --> 00:47:01,039
Hello.

1260
00:47:01,039 --> 00:47:01,880
Hi.

1261
00:47:01,880 --> 00:47:02,720
Yes.

1262
00:47:02,720 --> 00:47:07,000
Smile, wave, look friendly.

1263
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:08,640
Be non-threatening.

1264
00:47:08,640 --> 00:47:10,200
Kind of like lift up our hands,

1265
00:47:10,200 --> 00:47:12,000
you know, in the universal like.

1266
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:13,720
Look, no weapons in my hands.

1267
00:47:13,720 --> 00:47:14,559
Yeah.

1268
00:47:14,559 --> 00:47:15,400
Yeah.

1269
00:47:15,400 --> 00:47:19,680
You are now surrounded as they're pointing spears

1270
00:47:19,680 --> 00:47:20,519
at you.

1271
00:47:20,519 --> 00:47:23,679
And after a little while of them yelling

1272
00:47:23,679 --> 00:47:26,360
