1274
00:47:31,440 --> 00:47:36,079
just don't make any sudden movements, okay guys?

1275
00:47:36,079 --> 00:47:37,599
And some of them,

1276
00:47:37,599 --> 00:47:39,239
some of the warriors turned to look

1277
00:47:39,239 --> 00:47:41,960
where he was coming up and he walks out

1278
00:47:41,960 --> 00:47:45,119
and he says, I don't know

1279
00:47:45,119 --> 00:47:46,800
why they're acting like this guys.

1280
00:47:46,800 --> 00:47:47,639
Like really?

1281
00:47:47,799 --> 00:47:50,719
They're really normally very nice people.

1282
00:47:50,719 --> 00:47:51,839
As he's describing this,

1283
00:47:51,839 --> 00:47:54,719
one of the warriors comes up and knocks him out.

1284
00:47:54,719 --> 00:47:55,719
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

1285
00:47:55,719 --> 00:47:56,679
Thanks Larry.

1286
00:47:56,679 --> 00:48:01,000
In fact, all three of you are struck from behind

1287
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:02,319
