1337
00:49:57,160 --> 00:49:58,559
And you wake up,

1338
00:49:59,440 --> 00:50:00,960
you're unsure how long later,

1339
00:50:00,960 --> 00:50:04,039
but you are in a very small yurt,

1340
00:50:04,039 --> 00:50:05,200
tied up.

1341
00:50:05,200 --> 00:50:08,920
All of your belongings are out of reach

1342
00:50:08,920 --> 00:50:11,400
and you are being watched by one of the people

1343
00:50:11,400 --> 00:50:14,000
who was dressed up in some of the regalia.

