1348
00:50:23,360 --> 00:50:25,639
and why you're here and what you want from them.

1349
00:50:25,639 --> 00:50:27,519
Well, Larry, you know,

1350
00:50:28,480 --> 00:50:30,519
we are in search of a woman

1351
00:50:30,519 --> 00:50:34,360
who might have the location of the Dracorn.

